S.FORM: Byron Beck tatama, nalecuhan i Ellensburg, Washington, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw ayza. Byron Beck i 1967 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 2 ku uwac atu silsil 15, namapili' tu nu Chicago Bulls putiput. siwkay niza 1 bulad 25 demiad, 1945 a mihca, Byron Beck, miunduay. tatama ciniza , u kawaw niza sa u mimaliay. u Amilika a tademaw, sangelacay ku banges. u banggu niza sa 40(sepat a bataan). namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
